# Kubeconfig Paths

All kubeconfig files are in `~/ws/nkp/` (expanded: `/Users/deepak.muley/ws/nkp/`).

## Management Cluster

When running commands against the **management cluster** (dm-nkp-mgmt-1):

```bash
KUBECONFIG=/Users/deepak.muley/ws/nkp/dm-nkp-mgmt-1.conf
# or
--kubeconfig=/Users/deepak.muley/ws/nkp/dm-nkp-mgmt-1.conf
```

## Workload Clusters

When running commands against **workload clusters**:

| Cluster | Kubeconfig Path |
|---------|-----------------|
| dm-nkp-workload-1 | `/Users/deepak.muley/ws/nkp/dm-nkp-workload-1.kubeconfig` |
| dm-nkp-workload-2 | `/Users/deepak.muley/ws/nkp/dm-nkp-workload-2.kubeconfig` |

Examples:
```bash
# Workload 1
